REVIEW_UPDATE_QUEUE_URL=https://sqs.ap-southeast-1.amazonaws.com/123456789012/review-update-queue-dev
REVIEW_DELETION_QUEUE_URL=https://sqs.ap-southeast-1.amazonaws.com/123456789012/review-deletion-queue-dev

# User Account Events
